English: Use information in the environment to find [ITEM_ZONE]
Description: A short summary of a mission objective. In GTFO you seldom get a waypoint that indicates where you need to go - instead you need to actively look for signs and clues in the surroundings. Don't alter the "[ITEM_ZONE]" part, just put it in the gramatically correct position in the sentence.
